text: A viral Facebook post attributes to actor Clint Eastwood a long message that insults Democratic presidential nominee Joe Biden and alleges he is trying to destroy our wonderful country.
Says Clint Eastwood called Joe Biden an incompetent, lying, flip-flopping, insincere, double-talking, radical socialist.
